title: Holly Frey In Conversation With Seneca Women to Hear Winners: Kris McDaniel and Andi Gordon
itunes:title: Holly Frey In Conversation With Seneca Women to Hear Winners: Kris McDaniel and Andi Gordon
description:
Holly Frey, host of Stuff You Missed in History Class, sits down with Kris McDaniel and Andi Gordon, two winners of the Seneca Women to Hear: Search for the Next Great Female Podcasters.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
